        <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 p-0">
            <img src="~/Content/about.png" class="image-fit" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 padded-text">
            <h2>We are Community Oriented</h2>
            <p>The Cozy Bean is a brand of food and beverage from Toronto, Canada. It was founded by a group of 5 young coffee enthusiasts on November 2nd, 2021. They started the business together in a modest rented building located in the heart of downtown Toronto, at the intersection of Queens St. West and Bathurst St.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row p-0">
        <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 padded-text off-white">
            <h2>We Support Live Performance</h2>
            <p class="mb-5">To acquire a better connection with our community, we create an opportunity to do so with our live performance hours. Every Friday between 8 to 10 pm the stage is reserved for talented musicians. Every Sunday night we invite comedians to the stage to end the week on a perfect note.</p>
